  <brief_title>Oxaliplatin Combined With Fluorouracil and Leucovorin in Treating Patients With Recurrent or Metastatic Cancer of the Esophagus or Stomach</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Oxaliplatin in Combination With Fluorouracil and Leucovorin in Carcinoma of the Esophagus and Gastric Cardia</official_title>
